text:
Rude facility. My daughter and her friend were completely ignored by the staff. If you are under 21 don't bother patronizing this establishment. Last night my teenage daughter along with her friend took 2 young children they were babysitting to Yours Truly for a quick bite to eat. For over 20 minutes they were rudely ignored by the service staff. You have lost our business. May I remind you that several established restaurants are closing their doors. This failure normally starts with poor customer service  

Yours RUDELY;

Former customer
